ğŸ”¹ 7ï¸âƒ£ If Installing in Production (Recommended)

Lock version explicitly instead of using script:

curl -LO https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.20.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
tar -zxvf helm-v3.20.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz
mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/helm
helm version

